lead_paragraph: Spaniard Roberto Bautista Agut beat Serbian Viktor Troicki 6-3 6-4 on Sunday to win the inaugural Sofia Open and take his fourth ATP title.

headline.print_headline: Bautista Agut Wins Sofia Title After Beating Troicki
